		(uuid "7aa3637f-770b-4db3-ae35-a698f565790b")
	)
	(text "WiFi PCB trace antenna. Wavelength = 125mm.\n1/4 wavelength = 31.25mm\nA detailed doc on 2.4Ghz antenna traces:\nhttps://www.ti.com/lit/an/swra117d/swra117d.pdf\n\nPhil's Lab video on designing a PCB trace antenna:\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yxU_Kw2de08\n\nWe've ommitted hte matching filter network and ideal shape\ndue to low space availability, and WiFi not being part\nof this device's primary functionality."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 218.44 90.932 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "955a8032-0050-4486-9208-cfd609617144")
	)
	(text "This Temperature-compensated crystall\noscillator (TCXO) is the timing source for\nboth radios. Provides a stable frequency at\ndifferent temperatures compared to a normal crystal."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 35.56 101.6 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "ad9b2c8e-1ec3-40fa-9758-704b64976f03")
	)
	(text "3v3 regulator, since some FCs don't have a \n3v3 line. Also, an ELRS spec requirement."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 195.072 20.32 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "c16b5864-5818-416f-87b0-0e3c21a34632")
	)
	(text "Pull GPIO0 (boot pin) high, but allow it to be\ntied low to flash via UART, via bridging pads.\nPads have 2.54mm spacing, for bridging using\na 2-pin header bridged with a jumper."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 218.44 112.522 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "c56e2ac6-bec3-4394-bce8-53f870dff351")
	)
	(text "JST GH pin header (to FC)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 243.84 148.59 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "d01d12f5-8f09-42f7-82ed-9229d266c2d3")
	)
